  "body": "Here is an example. I want that contexts work in PageOne and PageTwo, but all subcomponents of SandBox won't get any context. How can I achieve it?\r\n\r\n```jsx\r\nconst ContextA = React.createContext('a');\r\nconst ContextB = React.createContext('b');\r\n\r\nclass App extends React.Component {\r\n  render() {\r\n    return (\r\n      <ContextA.Provider value=\"A\">\r\n           <ContextB.Provider value=\"B\">\r\n              <PageOne />\r\n              <PageTwo />\r\n              <SandBox>\r\n                  <SubPage />\r\n              </SandBox>\r\n           </ContextB.Provider>\r\n      </ContextA.Provider>\r\n    );\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction SubPage() {\r\n  return (\r\n    <ContextA.Consumer>\r\n      {a => (\r\n        <ContextB.Consumer>\r\n          {b => (\r\n            <Content />\r\n          )}\r\n        </ContextB.Consumer>\r\n      )}\r\n    </ContextA.Consumer>\r\n  );\r\n}\r\n```",
